_UcS7GvQhsIdpROs7CFsTt-XeHk9UhPnqjlz4w\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering testing approaches**\\n\\nI'm pondering whether helper classes still get included. There's something about how the access filter determines what's recorded and the user code filter defines the condition. Given the constraint to avoid creating source stubs or fake replacements for library types, it seems we can develop a custom plugin in the test package. I want to ensure that the dynamic-access report classes are kept one-to-one, and I can add ClassicConfigurationTest while keeping helper files acceptable.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Exploring potential removals**\\n\\nI’m considering whether something was removed in version 12.x. The reporter log indicates that the class exists, so it’s possible that Spring Boot is using Teams classes from flyway-nc. However, I’m thinking that coordinating with the core version 12.5.0 might be tricky if the Maven source is missing due to some issue. I also want to avoid modifying metadata, so I’ll keep that in mind as I write.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_tkiHVj3EHgEawd2LCxm5m2yg|fc_08bb24ef5c1ceea4016a05aa4a39d08196bc47293775515a2e", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.flywaydb/flyway-core/12.5.0/src/test/java/flyway/DynamicAccessChild.java", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage flyway;\n\npublic class DynamicAccessChild {\n\n    private Boolean flag;\n\n    public Boolean getFlag() {\n        return flag;\n    }\n\n    public void setFlag(final Boolean flag) {\n        this.flag = flag;\n    }\n}\n"}, "partialJson": "{\"path\":\"tests/src/org.flywaydb/flyway-core/12.5.0/src/test/java/flyway/DynamicAccessChild.java\",\"content\":\"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage flyway;\\n\\npublic class DynamicAccessChild {\\n\\n    private Boolean flag;\\n\\n    public Boolean getFlag() {\\n        return flag;\\n    }\\n\\n    public void setFlag(final Boolean flag) {\\n        this.flag = flag;\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1023, "output": 1494, "cacheRead": 44032, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 46549, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778756148240, "responseId": "resp_08bb24ef5c1ceea4016a05aa353480819697f2ffe326a8d819"}}
